            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>basa fillets</strong> into strips</p><p>Add the<strong> basa strips</strong> to the <strong>spiced cornflour</strong> and stir together until they're fully coated in the mixture</p>",
